NAME
    Catalyst::Authentication::Credential::FBConnect

VERSION
    version 0.03

SYNOPSIS
    In MyApp.pm

     use Catalyst qw/
          Authentication
          Session
          Session::Store::FastMmap
          Session::State::Cookie
     /;

    In myapp.conf

        <Plugin::Authentication>
            default_realm   facebook
            <realms>
                <facebook>
                    <credential>
                        class       FBConnect
                        api_key     my_app_key
                        secret      my_app_secret
                        app_name    my_app_name
                    </credential>
                </facebook>
            </realms>
        </Plugin::Authentication>

    In controller code,

      sub facebook : Local {
           my ($self, $c) = @_;

           if( $c->authenticate() ) {
                 #do something with $c->user
           }
      }

NAME
    Catalyst::Authentication::Credential::FBConnect - Facebook credential
    for Catalyst::Plugin::Authentication framework.

VERSION
    0.01

USER METHODS
    $c->user->session_uid
    $c->user->session_key
    $c->user->session_expires

